<Defs>


  <ThingDef ParentName="AnimalThingBase" >
  
   <defName>Sovereign_GizkaRace</defName>
    <label>Gizka</label>
    <description>A diminutive reptile found in all types of climates. The Gizka is a pest whose notoriety for possessing a voracious hunger for anything even remotely edible is only outstripped by their reputation of extreme docility. Their innate passivity not only makes them a great companion, but also makes them an easy target for a hunter, as they will never fight back and never run away, even if they are being attacked. In fact, the only reason they are any is due to their adaptability to almost any climate and nearly ludicrous reproduction rate, just barely managing to outstrip the rate at which they are hunted and killed. The Gizka's location of origin is unknown, as it seems to have a knack for spreading onto other planets by sneaking onto spaceships, whether they manage to make it to their destination or are jettisoned onto a remote rimworld.</description>
    <uiIconScale>1.5</uiIconScale>
	
	
    <statBases>
      <MoveSpeed>6.0</MoveSpeed>
      <MarketValue>50</MarketValue>
      <ComfyTemperatureMin>-5</ComfyTemperatureMin>
	  <ComfyTemperatureMax>60</ComfyTemperatureMax>
	  <ToxicEnvironmentResistance>1</ToxicEnvironmentResistance>
	  
	  <Wildness>0</Wildness>
    </statBases>
	
